captions.text: - Yeah, I mean I'm just a regular
guy that's never met a puppy.
I don't know why people thinks that weird.
- I'm here to meet some pup-pups.
- I feel like I'm gonna just turn
into a child when I see them.
- Since I haven't had a dog I feel
like something's missing in my life.

- I am concerned that I may
have a puppy bite my mustache.
- I'm excited to meet any puppy right now.
- These puppies are total divas right now.
They just don't want to play with me.
- Well, I mean, I think everything's
cuter when it's a baby, right?
- Whoah, this dude is so tiny.

- Uh-oh, he's got a piece
of bark or something.
- I'm in love with this dog.
Look at you, you're so happy.
- I kind of bonded with these dogs.
they're just so full of life.
- It makes me want to order one right now.

- It's uh, it's like
being with an old friend.

- I believe a pup-pup
will choose me some day.

And when the call is
made, I will answer it.
- Uh, my name is uh, like Sean.
Puppies are not a big deal.
I guess someone could love this, you know.
